  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Shikigami Clan, Level 8+</p><p>The things you make, are far more deadly than most gives them credit for. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p><p><br />• When you cast a Shikigami Hijutsu, you may spend 5 Chakra. <br />If you do, that jutsu can gain the benefit of one of the Paper Expert clan features 7th level effect, as if the jutsu cast was one of the chosen Ninja tools (Select one of the ninja tools when you use this Feat, you do not spend a bonus action or any additional chakra to satisfy the requirements of this Feat.) This bonus can only be applied once per casting. </p><p><br />• Paper based ninja tools listed within your Papercraft Clan feature, has their save DC increase by 1, and deal an additional die of damage. </p><p><br />• When you would create ninja tools using the Papercraft clan feature, you may always create 2 additional of any one tool.</p>",
